<paragraph base="F3903600" principles="no" id="IAS01_94"><paranum>94</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 1"/><data name="paranum" value="94"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS01_P0510">An entity may present <xref base="F3903067" href="IAS01_7_reclassificationadjustments.dita">reclassification adjustments<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0317"/></ph></xref> in the statement(s) of profit or loss and other comprehensive income or in the <xref base="F3903012" href="IAS01_7_notes.dita">notes<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0263"/></ph></xref>.              An entity presenting reclassification adjustments in the notes presents the items of <xref base="F3903039" href="IAS01_7_othercomprehensiveincome.dita">other comprehensive income<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0276"/></ph></xref> after any related reclassification adjustments.</p></body></paragraph>